  <body>
    <para styleclass="Body Text2-Note"><table styleclass="PopupTable" rowcount="1" colcount="1">
      <tr style="vertical-align:top">
        <td>
          <para styleclass="Popup Box"><text styleclass="Popup Box2">Conjugate-Cam </text><text styleclass="VariableName-small">definition</text>: a Body-Closed Cam in which a minimum of two(2) <text styleclass="Popup Box-Elements">2D-Cams</text> on a <text styleclass="Popup Box-Elements">Part</text>, that are each in continuous contact a different &#160;<text styleclass="VariableName-small">Cam-follower Roller</text>, which are on a different <text styleclass="Element">Part</text>. </para>
          <para styleclass="Popup Box">A <text styleclass="VariableName-small">Groove Cam</text> is also special case of a <text styleclass="VariableName-small">Conjugate Cam</text>. </para>
          <para styleclass="Popup Box">Another term is <text styleclass="VariableName-small">Body-Closed Cam</text>. </para>
          <para styleclass="Normal"><line style="height:1px; color:#993300;" /></para>
          <para styleclass="SeeAlso-small">See <link displaytype="text" defaultstyle="true" type="topiclink" href="MD-Command-AddConjugateCam-FB">Machine-Elements menu &gt; Add Conjugate Cam FB</link></para>
        </td>
      </tr>
    </table></para>
